"Most low and medium risk vulnerabilities have been fixed, but business risks are greater than in the past, says a report in this issue of Computer Fraud & Security. Dr Andrea Pasquinucci believes the security level of systems and applications has greatly improved. But despite the improvement of ICT security, the financial risks from systems are much higher with fraud being the largest security concern. He recommends practical techniques to find the weakest points and secure them. Andrea Pasquinucci examines what risk means to different sized companies"
